---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@styles/pagination.scss";
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import singleImg from "@assets/blog/single_hero.png";
import ButtonPrimary from "@components/ButtonPrimary";
import { links } from "@scripts/links";
---

<Layout>
  <section>
    <div class="hero intro-anim">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="pagination paragraph-1 intro-anim">
          <span>home</span> > <span>unitree go2</span> > <strong>
            Customize your Go2</strong
          >
        </p>
        <h1 class="h1 intro-anim">Unitree B-W Showcased at ICRA 2023 London</h1>
        <Picture
          src={singleImg}
          alt="Single Blog Page Image"
          class={"intro-anim"}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="details paragraph-1 intro-anim">
      <div class="info">
        <p>March 17,2025</p>
        <span></span>
        <p>7 min</p>
        <span></span>
        <p>By Joe Doe</p>
      </div>
      <div class="share">
        <p>Share</p>
        <a class="border-gradient" target="_blank">
          <img src="/icons/link.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <a class="border-gradient" href={links.linkedin} target="_blank">
          <img src="/icons/linkedin.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <a class="border-gradient" href={links.x} target="_blank">
          <img src="/icons/x.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <a class="border-gradient" href={links.facebook} target="_blank">
          <img src="/icons/fb.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-container intro-anim">
      <div class="post paragraph-1 text-start">
        <p>
          Unitree Robotics participated in ICRA for the sixth consecutive year.
          Unitree Robotics exhibited Go1, B1, A1, and other quadruped robots at
          ICRA. Unitree is a world-renowned robotics company that focuses on
          self-development. LONDON, ENGLAND / ACCESSWIRE / June 2, 2023 /Â On May
          29, ICRA 2023, the International Conference on Robotics and
          Automation, was held in London, UK, which is the largest and most
          influential international academic conference in the field of robotics
          organized by the International Institute of Electrical and Electronics
          Engineering (IEEE). Unitree Robotics, a leader in the foot-based
          robotics industry, was invited to participate in this international
          event to showcase the innovative power of Chinese technology companies
          to the world.
        </p>
        <p>
          At this year's ICRA 2023, Unitree Robotics officially launched the
          Unitree B-W wheeled robot, which not only attracted a large number of
          visitors to stop by and take photos, but also added fresh colors to
          this year's ICRA. Several top robotics companies around the world
          participated in the showcase. In addition to Unitree Robotics, seven
          other exhibitors brought Unitree Robotics quadruped robots to ICRA,
          highlighting Unitree Robotics' leading position in robotics technology
          and strong leadership in the field. ICRA 2023 hosted a number of
          robotics challenges on site, and the Quadruped Robotics Challenge QRC
          was the first of a series of challenges, covering a range of events
          from Quadruped Robotics Remote Control Race to Autonomous Traversal of
          Challenging Terrain, and Unitree Robotics became the exclusive sponsor
          of Quadruped Robotics in Greater China with its outstanding
          technological strength. In addition, the competition also attracted
          many world-renowned universities and research institutions from
          Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT), Carnegie Mellon
          University, Korea Institute of Science and Technology (KAIST), the
          University of Hong Kong, Heriot-Watt University, Clemson University,
          etc., and Unitree Robotics provided technical support and services to
          the participating teams, contributing actively to the development of
          the robotics field. Unitree Robotics has made a positive contribution
          to the development of the robotics field.
        </p>
        <p>
          In addition to a wide range of on-site challenges, well-known
          technology companies such as Boston Dynamics, Dyson, Baidu, IIT and
          PAL Robotics were also on hand to showcase their latest technologies
          in the field of robotics.
        </p>
        <p>
          Robots have long since turned from fantasy in science fiction movies
          into reality and have permeated all walks of life, and intelligent
          robots will accompany people's lives in the future, following them
          like a shadow and being everywhere. Unitree Robotics has been invited
          to participate in ICRA for six consecutive years, and every year,
          Unitree Robotics will continue to put technological innovation in
          first place as the leader of the foot robot industry in China, and
          will continue to make breakthroughs and develop continuously to lead
          the global foot robot industry to new heights.
        </p>
        <div class="share">
          <p>Share</p>
          <a class="border-gradient" target="_blank">
            <img src="/icons/link.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <a class="border-gradient" href={links.linkedin} target="_blank">
            <img src="/icons/linkedin.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <a class="border-gradient" href={links.x} target="_blank">
            <img src="/icons/x.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <a class="border-gradient" href={links.facebook} target="_blank">
            <img src="/icons/fb.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="in-touch">
        <div>
          <p class="subtitle-3 color-white">
            Subscribe to our newsletter for daily industry insights
          </p>
          <form class="field">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" />
            <ButtonPrimary
              client:load
              content="submit"
              className="inside-input"
            />
          </form>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="subtitle-3 color-white">Follow Us</p>
          <span class="paragraph-1">
            Get the latest news and industry Inspiration.
          </span>
          <div class="socials">
            <a href={links.x} target="_blank">
              <img src="/icons/x.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <a href={links.youtube} target="_blank">
              <img src="/icons/youtube.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <a href={links.facebook} target="_blank">
              <img src="/icons/fb.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .share {
    display: grid;
    grid-auto-flow: column;
    grid-auto-columns: max-content;
    gap: calc(var(--fs) * 1.13);
    align-items: center;
    p {
      margin-right: calc(var(--fs) * 5);
    }
    a {
      width: calc(var(--fs) * 3.4375);
      height: calc(var(--fs) * 3.4375);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      img {
        width: 40%;
        height: 40%;
        object-fit: contain;
        z-index: 1;
      }
    }
  }
  section {
    padding: 0 calc(var(--hor-padding)) calc(var(--fs) * 10);
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      position: relative;
      &::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        z-index: -1;
        bottom: 0;
        right: 0;
        transform: translate(50%, 30%);
        width: 100vw;
        height: 50vw;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(var(--MAIN-BLUE), #00000000 50%);
        opacity: 0.35;
      }
      &::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, 0%);
        background-color: #767676;
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
      }
      .content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr max-content;
        grid-template-rows: max-content 1fr;
        place-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 10vh;
        & > * {
          grid-column: 1 / 2;
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
        }
        .pagination {
          margin: 0;
          grid-row: 1 / 2;
          align-self: flex-start;
        }
        h1 {
          grid-row: 2 / 3;
          align-self: flex-start;
          margin-top: 5vh;
        }

        picture {
          width: calc(var(--fs) * 44.375);
          height: calc(var(--fs) * 25);
          border-radius: calc(var(--fs) * 1.25);
          overflow: hidden;
          grid-row: 1 / 3;
          grid-column: 2 / 3;
          img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
          }
        }
      }
    }

    .details {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 2.75);
      .info {
        display: grid;
        grid-auto-flow: column;
        grid-auto-columns: max-content;
        gap: calc(var(--fs) * 4.44 / 2);
        align-items: center;
        span {
          width: 1px;
          height: calc(var(--fs) * 2.4);
          background-color: #767676;
        }
      }
    }
    .post-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr calc(var(--fs) * 32.9375);
      align-items: start;
      margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 8);
      gap: calc(var(--fs) * 9);
      .post {
        display: grid;
        grid-auto-flow: row;
        grid-auto-rows: max-content;
        gap: calc(var(--fs) * 3);
        .share {
          display: none;
        }
      }
      .in-touch {
        div {
          .field {
            input {
              color: #757575;
              font-size: var(--fs);
              font-style: normal;
              font-weight: 300;
              line-height: 134%; /* 1.34rem */
              text-transform: capitalize;
            }
          }
          .paragraph-1 {
            margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
            width: calc(var(--fs) * 15);
            display: block;
          }
          & > * {
            text-align: left;
          }
          &:first-of-type {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #767676;
            padding-bottom: calc(var(--fs) * 4.75);
          }
          &:last-of-type {
            margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 5);
            .socials {
              display: grid;
              grid-auto-flow: column;
              grid-auto-columns: max-content;
              gap: calc(var(--fs) * 2.37);
              align-items: center;
              padding: 0;
              border: unset;
              margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
              a {
                img {
                  height: calc(var(--fs) * 1.66);
                  width: auto;
                  object-fit: contain;
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (orientation: portrait) {
    .share {
      gap: calc(var(--fs) * 1);
      align-items: center;
      p {
        margin-right: calc(var(--fs) * 1);
      }
      a {
        width: calc(var(--fs) * 2.55);
        height: calc(var(--fs) * 2.55);
      }
    }
    section {
      padding: calc(var(--top-space) * 1.5) calc(var(--hor-padding) * 2)
        calc(var(--fs) * 5);
      .hero {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        height: initial;
        padding-bottom: calc(var(--fs) * 2.5);
        &::before {
          content: "";
          position: absolute;
          z-index: -1;
          bottom: 50%;
          right: 50%;
          transform: translate(50%, 60%);
          width: 120vw;
          height: 120vw;
          border-radius: 50%;
          background: radial-gradient(var(--MAIN-BLUE), #00000000 50%);
          opacity: 0.5;
        }
        &::after {
          content: "";
          position: absolute;
          bottom: 0;
          left: 50%;
          transform: translate(-50%, 50%);
          background-color: #767676;
          width: 100%;
          height: 1px;
        }
        .content {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          justify-self: flex-start;
          margin: 0;
          h1 {
            grid-row: 2 / 3;
            align-self: flex-start;
            margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 3.5);
          }

          picture {
            width: 100%;
            height: calc(var(--fs) * 25);
            border-radius: calc(var(--fs) * 2.3);
            margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 5);
          }
        }
      }

      .details {
        margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 3);
        .info {
          gap: calc(var(--fs) * 1);
          span {
            width: 1px;
            height: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
          }
        }
      }
      .post-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 100%;
        grid-auto-flow: row;
        grid-auto-rows: max-content;
        margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 6);
        gap: calc(var(--fs) * 6);
        .post {
          gap: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
        }
        .in-touch {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
          align-items: start;
          div {
            grid-row: 1/2;
            margin: 0 !important;
            border: unset !important;
            display: grid;
            grid-auto-flow: row;
            grid-auto-rows: max-content;
            gap: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
            & > * {
              margin: 0 !important;
            }
            .field {
              input {
                color: #757575;
                font-size: var(--fs);
                font-style: normal;
                font-weight: 300;
                line-height: 134%; /* 1.34rem */
                text-transform: capitalize;
              }
            }
            .paragraph-1 {
              margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 0);
              width: 100%;
              display: block;
            }
            & > * {
              text-align: left;
            }
            &:first-of-type {
              border-bottom: 1px solid #767676;
              padding-bottom: calc(var(--fs) * 4.75);
            }
            &:last-of-type {
              margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 5);
              & > * {
                grid-row: auto;
              }
              .socials {
                a {
                  img {
                    height: calc(var(--fs) * 1.66);
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }

    @media (max-aspect-ratio: 0.625) {
      section {
        padding: calc(var(--top-space) * 1.5) calc(var(--hor-padding) * 1)
          calc(var(--fs) * 5);
        .hero {
          &::before {
            bottom: 0%;
            right: 0%;
            transform: translate(50%, 50%);
            width: 180vw;
            height: 180vw;
            background: radial-gradient(var(--MAIN-BLUE), #00000000 50%);
            opacity: 0.35;
          }
          &::after {
            background-color: #767676;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
          }
          .content {
            h1 {
              grid-row: 2 / 3;
              align-self: flex-start;
              margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 1.5);
            }

            picture {
              height: calc(var(--fs) * 15);
              border-radius: calc(var(--fs) * 1.25);
              margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 5);
            }
          }
        }

        .details {
          margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
          width: 100%;
          .info {
            gap: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
            width: 100%;
            place-items: center;
            place-content: center;
            span {
              width: 1px;
              height: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
            }
          }
          .share {
            gap: calc(var(--fs) * 1);
            align-items: center;
            display: none;
            p {
              margin-right: calc(var(--fs) * 1);
            }
            a {
              width: calc(var(--fs) * 2.55);
              height: calc(var(--fs) * 2.55);
            }
          }
        }
        .post-container {
          margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 2.5);
          gap: calc(var(--fs) * 4.5);
          .post {
            gap: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
            .share {
              display: grid;
              place-items: center;
              place-content: center;
              margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 3);
              & > * {
                grid-column: auto;
                grid-row: 2/3;
              }
              p {
                grid-column: 1 / 5;
                grid-row: 1/2;
                text-align: center;
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
              }
            }
          }
          .in-touch {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 100%;
            grid-auto-flow: row;
            grid-auto-rows: max-content;
            align-items: start;
            & > * {
              grid-column: 1/2 !important;
              grid-row: auto !important;
            }
            div {
              grid-row: 1/2;
              margin: 0 !important;
              border: unset !important;
              display: grid;
              grid-auto-flow: row;
              grid-auto-rows: max-content;
              gap: calc(var(--fs) * 2);
              & > * {
                margin: 0 !important;
              }
              .field {
                input {
                  color: #757575;
                  font-size: var(--fs);
                  font-style: normal;
                  font-weight: 300;
                  line-height: 134%; /* 1.34rem */
                  text-transform: capitalize;
                }
              }
              .paragraph-1 {
                margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 0);
                width: 100%;
                display: block;
              }
              & > * {
                text-align: left;
              }
              &:first-of-type {
                border-bottom: 1px solid #767676;
                padding-bottom: calc(var(--fs) * 4.75);
              }
              &:last-of-type {
                margin-top: calc(var(--fs) * 5);
                & > * {
                  grid-row: auto;
                }
                .socials {
                  a {
                    img {
                      height: calc(var(--fs) * 1.66);
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
